sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Go Server
    participant St as Stripe
    participant DS as Firestore
    participant E as Resend

    Note over B,S: Payment Initiation
    B->>S: POST /finance/make-a-payment {agreementId, amountPence}
    S->>St: Create PaymentIntent
    St-->>S: clientSecret
    S->>DS: Save PaymentRecord (PENDING)
    S->>DS: Log AuditEvent
    S-->>B: {clientSecret}

    Note over B,St: Client-Side Payment
    B->>St: confirmCardPayment (Stripe Elements)
    St-->>B: Payment result

    Note over St,S: Webhook Processing
    St->>S: POST /api/stripe/webhook (payment_intent.succeeded)
    S->>S: Verify signature
    S->>DS: Check idempotency (webhookEventId)
    S->>DS: Update status to COMPLETED
    S->>DS: Log AuditEvent
    S->>E: Send confirmation email
    S-->>St: 200 OK
